{"type":"message","id":"3af7e9be","parentId":"3268bc3c","timestamp":"2026-05-05T07:07:02.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to try voice bidirectional communication. They're saying their computer isn't high-spec. Let me first check what's available and then install what's needed.\n\nFrom what I can see:\n1. No Whisper installed\n2. Sherpa-ONNX skill is available but disabled\n3. They have 4 CPU cores\n\nLet me check more about their system specs and what's available to install.","thinkingSignature":"2de7de28fe51602845258aca3b573490ed3242b4ced89ca7724aed5f42a9942b"},{"type":"text","text":"好，先看看你的实际配置，然后选最轻量的方案。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7j9a7lzgoaub_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== CPU ===\"; lscpu | grep -E \"Model name|CPU\\(s\\)|Thread|Core\"; echo \"=== 内存 ===\"; free -h; echo \"=== 磁盘 ===\"; df -h / | tail -1; echo \"=== GPU ===\"; lspci 2>/dev/null | grep -iE \"vga|3d|display|nvidia|amd\" | head -5; nvidia-smi 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":154,"output":218,"cacheRead":12896,"cacheWrite":12486,"totalTokens":25754,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777964814002,"responseId":"0648ca0f5e622e9f3e6b1271b57b34f0"}}
