{"type":"message","id":"82ff0f5c","parentId":"46afa7bb","timestamp":"2026-05-05T07:07:21.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so:\n- Intel i5-6300U (2 cores, 4 threads) - very low-end CPU\n- 3.7GB RAM (very low)\n- No NVIDIA GPU\n- 117GB SSD with 52GB free\n\nThis is a low-end machine. Let me think about what to install:\n\n1. **ASR (Speech-to-Text)**: \n   - Whisper CPU-only will be slow on this. `faster-whisper` with INT8 quantization would be better.\n   - With only 3.7GB RAM and 2 cores, I should use the smallest model (tiny or base) for testing.\n   - The `openai-whisper` skill is available (disabled). Or I could install `faster-whisper` directly.\n\n2. **TTS**:\n   - Sherpa-ONNX is already installed (the skill exists and there's a `sherpa-onnx-tts` skill listed in config)\n   - Or I could use Piper (lightweight, CPU-friendly)\n\nGiven the low RAM (3.7GB), I need to be very careful. Let me:\n1. Install `faster-whisper` with the tiny/base model (smallest, fastest for CPU)\n2. Check sherpa-onnx availability\n3. Configure the feishu channel to handle voice messages\n\nBut wait - for receiving voice (user → AI), the feishu plugin needs to support it. \n\nI need to understand how the feishu channel currently processes incoming voice messages and what the sherpa-onnx-tts skill actually provides. This is critical for the voice pipeline to work - I need to know if the feishu plugin can already handle voice messages and route them to ASR, or if that's where the gap is.","thinkingSignature":"91920aa5cda3f905f4c5bdd71e255475b498c039e8d05cbf4396b3a2a6c8cd99"},{"type":"text","text":"配置确实偏低：\n- **CPU**: i5-6300U（2核4线程，轻量级）\n- **RAM**: 3.7GB（比较紧张）\n- **GPU**: 集显 HD 520（不能跑大模型）\n\n这种情况下我建议用 **最小模型先试**。方案：\n\n| 模块 | 方案 | 内存 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| ASR（你→我） | faster-whisper tiny | ~300MB | 最轻量，CPU可用 |\n| TTS（我→你） | sherpa-onnx | ~200MB | 你已装，极轻 |\n\n开始装：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4e8rfdhro9kp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pip install faster-whisper -q 2>&1 | tail -5","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4375,"output":566,"cacheRead":21556,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26497,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777964823292,"responseId":"0648ca17fd70744066c62bfa87d3568d"}}
