{"type":"message","id":"e7869a85","parentId":"4a147262","timestamp":"2026-05-05T08:08:16.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The MiniMax API key only has access to chat models (M2.7, M2.5, M2.1 etc). It doesn't have TTS models access. The TTS API is separate.\n\nLet me try to download a local TTS model. Kokoro is a good small TTS model for sherpa-onnx. Let me try to download it.Actually, let me think about what's fastest right now. The user wants to try sending a voice message. Let me:\n\n1. Download a small TTS model for sherpa-onnx\n2. Use it to generate audio\n3. Send via Feishu message\n\nLet me check if there are pre-built sherpa-onnx TTS models I can download quickly.","thinkingSignature":"ca3b4005379349f82867e3c5731bc5c31b75bd20356171e43127432efcb37965"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9bzx6oea89im_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check available Kokoro models from sherpa-onnx\n# Kokoro is a small, fast TTS model\nls /tmp/sherpa-onnx* 2>/dev/null || echo \"no cached models\"\n\n# Check disk space for downloading\ndf -h /tmp | tail -1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17987,"output":242,"cacheRead":21559,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39788,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777968487374,"responseId":"0648d867386a50381ac33c7cdeaf5fb3"}}
