{"type":"message","id":"5b67bebb","parentId":"3d44ac86","timestamp":"2026-05-05T08:09:58.891Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see that MiniMax TTS uses `https://api.minimax.io` (not minimaxi.com). And the model names are like `speech-02-hd`, `speech-02-turbo`, etc. And the voice IDs include Chinese voices like \"Chinese (Mandarin)_Warm_Girl\".\n\nBut the API key I see in the config is for `api.minimaxi.com` which is for the chat API. The TTS API at `api.minimax.io` might need a different API key.\n\nLet me try to call the MiniMax TTS API with the correct endpoint and see what happens. The baseUrl should be `https://api.minimax.io` and the model should be something like `speech-02-hd`.","thinkingSignature":"74ee78c7c34d1c1936b036cfad70751ab44bf9bad744b22e68ee984c874e79cb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tbw7lgn12tms_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try MiniMax TTS API with the correct endpoint and model\nAPI_KEY=\"sk-cp-gtdRxxiZ_Qu_-9GM0xBF6UpeDvsYl8cPe4Y9mA-Xiy2GO8eBJSNPftqJdMb0Fl9OZAkY6sQR868fRUhTBV7OtwKyDfu-DzegI9-cDZERwbQGf3C5Wuvs38c\"\n\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/t2a_v2\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"speech-02-hd\",\n    \"text\": \"嗨 HALEI，我是 KIIT。这是一条测试语音，看看效果怎么样。\",\n    \"voice_setting\": {\n      \"voice_id\": \"Chinese (Mandarin)_Warm_Girl\",\n      \"speed\": 1,\n      \"vol\": 1,\n      \"pitch\": 0\n    },\n    \"audio_setting\": {\n      \"format\": \"mp3\",\n      \"sample_rate\": 32000\n    }\n  }' 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20865,"output":446,"cacheRead":21559,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777968589002,"responseId":"0648d8cdc55990988b2f8f564a52e80d"}}
