{"type":"message","id":"1e38ee0a","parentId":"ab89f283","timestamp":"2026-05-05T12:52:26.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The logs show \"Channel login failed: Error: Channel wecom does not support login\". This means the wecom channel exists but the login failed because the channel doesn't support login. This is the current state:\n\n- The wecom channel is registered (so \"unknown channel id\" might have been from an earlier version)\n- But wecom doesn't support login, which is needed for the bot to receive messages\n\nThe \"二维码多次失效\" error means the QR code login for wecom has been tried too many times and is now locked.\n\nSo the issue with wecom is:\n1. The wecom plugin exists but requires re-authentication (QR code)\n2. The QR code has been invalidated due to too many failed attempts\n\n\n3. I need to check if there's a way to re-authenticate or reset the wecom connection, and also look at whether the wecom channel ID is actually \"wecom\" or if it's registered under a different name in the plugin manifest.\n\nThe \"二维码多次失效，连接流程已停止\" error is the real blocker—the QR code has been tried too many times and needs to be reinitiated. The core problem is that the wecom channel exists but can't authenticate because the QR code session has expired and needs to be restarted from scratch.","thinkingSignature":"85257eac70b7fdde4c3850f9c32067597f09a8b3fabac7458cb2624c00c6d23f"},{"type":"text","text":"查清楚了。企业微信的 channel 存在，但状态有问题：\n\n- **\"二维码多次失效\"** — QR 码认证过期/次数过多，需要重新授权\n- **\"Channel wecom does not support login\"** — wecom 不支持扫码登录方式（说明这个插件的认证方式不对）\n\n**根本原因：** 企业微信插件没正确配置或者认证过期了。不是 Gateway 的问题，是 WeCom 侧的问题。\n\n你要：\n1. **重新配置 WeCom** — 需要重新跑一遍接入流程\n2. **暂时不管** — 飞书够用\n\n想继续折腾 WeCom 的话，告诉我要不要搞。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52940,"output":392,"cacheRead":21934,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75266,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777985531347,"responseId":"06491afcb1be7e98de3b0ec2af1d07a4"}}
