re behind a reverse proxy, set gateway.trustedProxies and forward X-Forwarded-For/X-Real-IP.\n[WARN] 20:39:13 Config warnings:\n- plugins.entries.openclaw-weixin: plugin openclaw-weixin: installed plugin package requires compiled runtime output for TypeScript entry index.ts: expected ./dist\n[WARN] 20:39:15 startup model warmup timed out after 5000ms; continuing without waiting\n[ERROR] 20:39:17 Invalid config at /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json:\\n- messages.groupChat: Unrecognized key: \"visibleReplies\"\n- plugins: Unrecognized key: \"bundledDiscovery\"\n[INFO] 20:39:22 \n[INFO] 20:39:22 \n[INFO] 20:39:22 \n[INFO] 20:39:22 \n[INFO] 20:39:22 \n[ERROR] 20:39:22 \n[WARN] 20:39:22 \n[ERROR] 20:39:22 [38;5;167mChannel login failed: Error: Failed to start login: TypeError: fetch failed[39m\n[WARN] 20:39:45 Loopback connection with non-local Host header. Treating it as remote. If you're behind a reverse proxy, set gateway.trustedProxies and forward X-Forwarded-For/X-Real-IP.\n[ERROR] 20:40:09 feishu[kiit]: failed to dispatch message: TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'registry')\n[WARN] 20:50:56 tools.profile (full) allowlist contains unknown entries (wecom_mcp). These entries won't match any tool unless the plugin is enabled.\n[WARN] 20:50:56 tools.allow allowlist contains unknown entries (wecom_mcp). These entries won't match any tool unless the plugin is enabled.\n[WARN] 20:51:04 liveness warning: reasons=event_loop_delay interval=30s eventLoopDelayP99Ms=131.1 eventLoopDelayMaxMs=3424.6 eventLoopUtilization=0.334 cpuCoreRatio=0.377 active=1 waiting=0 queued"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777985626400}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e286e46","parentId":"2226fff7","timestamp":"2026-05-05T12:53:57.582Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The logs show multiple issues:\n\n1. **Gateway connection failures** — The agent keeps failing to connect with \"device identity required\". This is happening repeatedly.\n\n2. **Feishu login failed** — \"Failed to start login: TypeError: fetch failed\" — Feishu login process is failing\n\n3. **Feishu dispatch failed** — \"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'registry')\" — This seems like a code issue in the feishu plugin\n\n4. **Event loop delay** — `eventLoopDelayP99Ms=131.1` and `eventLoopDelayMaxMs=3424.6` — The event loop is significantly delayed (3.4 seconds max), which indicates the system is under heavy load or there are blocking operations. This could cause slow responses.\n   \n5. **Memory pressure** — With only 3.7GB available and CPU at 33% utilization, the system is likely struggling to handle these concurrent operations.\n\nThe feishu plugin itself appears to have a code bug where it's trying to access a registry that doesn't exist, which is preventing messages from being dispatched properly.\n\nThe \"device identity required\" error is also blocking gateway connections. I should run the openclaw-doctor script to get a full diagnostic of what's broken.","thinkingSignature":"1844e243a1d1e83e22c45ebf356c9054dabfb78b81e8a0e59e83611be4f19534"},{"type":"text","text":"检查到多个问题。先跑一遍完整诊断。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ielf4vpzscb0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-doctor/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55203,"output":316,"cacheRead":21934,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77453,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777985626412,"responseId":"06491b5a3826b90d8d583159046fca12"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc71acb4","parentId":"6e286e46","timestamp":"2026-05-05T12:53:57.786Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ielf4vpzscb0_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: openclaw-doctor\ndescription: OpenClaw 诊断与维修工具。用于排查和修复 OpenClaw Gateway、通道、模型配置等问题。当用户报告 OpenClaw 无响应、功能异常、连接失败时使用此 Skill。\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    triggers:\n      - \"openclaw 没响应\"\n      - \"gateway 没响应\"\n      - \"openclaw 故障\"\n      - \"openclaw 维修\"\n      - \"openclaw doctor\"\n      - \"openclaw 问题\"\n      - \"openclaw 错误\"\n      - \"通道连接失败\"\n      - \"飞书没响应\"\n      - \"微信没响应\"\n---\n\n# OpenClaw Doctor - 诊断与维修\n\n当用户报告 OpenClaw 相关问题时，使用此 Skill 进行排查和修复。\n\n## 诊断流程\n\n### 1. 检查 Gateway 状态\n\n首先检查 Gateway 是否运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n检查端口是否监听：\n\n```bash\nss -tlnp | grep 18789\n```\n\n### 2. 检查进程\n\n```bash\nps aux | grep openclaw\n```\n\n### 3. 查看日志\n\n```bash\nopenclaw logs --limit 50\n```\n\n或者查看文件日志：\n\n```bash\ntail -100 /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-$(date +%Y-%m-%d).log\n```\n\n### 4. 运行 doctor\n\n```bash\nopenclaw doctor\nopenclaw doctor --repair\n```\n\n### 5. 检查通道状态\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channels status\n```\n\n### 6. 检查模型状态\n\n```bash\nopenclaw models status\n```\n\n## 常见问题与解决方案\n\n### 问题：Gateway 无响应\n\n**诊断：**\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:18789/\n```\n\n**解决方案：**\n```bash\n# 重启 Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n\n# 或者重新安装服务\nopenclaw gateway uninstall\nopenclaw gateway install\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n### 问题：飞书通道连接失败\n\n**诊断：**\n```bash\nopenclaw channels logs --channel feishu --lines 50\n```\n\n**解决方案：**\n```bash\n# 重新登录飞书\nopenclaw channels logout --channel feishu\nopenclaw channels login --channel feishu\n\n# 检查配置\nopenclaw config get channels.feishu\n```\n\n### 问题：微信通道 session 过期\n\n**日志特征：**\n```\nweixin getUpdates: session expired (errcode -14), pausing bot for 60 min\n```\n\n**解决方案：**\n```bash\n# 需要重新获取微信登录态\n# 查看配置\nopenclaw config get channels.openclaw-weixin\n```\n\n### 问题：模型认证失败\n\n**诊断：**\n```bash\nopenclaw models status --probe\n```\n\n**解决方案：**\n```bash\n# 重新配置模型认证\nopenclaw models auth add\n\n# 或者使用 setup-token\nopenclaw models auth setup-token --provider anthropic\n```\n\n### 问题：端口被占用\n\n**诊断：**\n```bash\nlsof -i :18789\n```\n\n**解决方案：**\n```bash\n# 杀掉占用进程\nkill <pid>\n\n# 或者使用 --force 启动\nopenclaw gateway run --force\n```\n\n### 问题：配置文件错误\n\n**诊断：**\n```bash\nopenclaw config validate\n```\n\n**解决方案：**\n```bash\n# 查看配置\nopenclaw config file\nopenclaw config get\n\n# 重置配置\nopenclaw reset --scope config --yes\n```\n\n## 维修命令速查\n\n| 操作 | 命令 |\n|------|------|\n| 检查状态 | `openclaw gateway status` |\n| 重启 Gateway | `openclaw gateway restart` |\n| 查看日志 | `openclaw logs --limit 50` |\n| 通道状态 | `openclaw channels status` |\n| 模型状态 | `openclaw models status` |\n| 诊断修复 | `openclaw doctor --repair` |\n| 通道日志 | `openclaw channels logs --lines 50` |\n\n## 自动修复\n\n当需要自动修复时，执行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw doctor --repair --force\n```\n\n这将尝试自动修复常见问题。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777985637786}}
