{"type":"message","id":"d0ab1bed","parentId":"4c3dd834","timestamp":"2026-05-05T13:22:58.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the issues:\n\n1. **feishu `groupPolicy: allowlist` with empty `groupAllowFrom`** - all group messages are silently dropped\n2. **wecom channel** - `channels.wecom: unknown channel id: wecom` (the plugin's channel ID isn't \"wecom\")\n3. **stale plugin references** - `wecom-openclaw-plugin` referenced but seems to not be properly installed\n4. **duplicated feishu plugin** - two feishu plugin entries\n\nLet me fix these:\n1. Set `groupPolicy: \"open\"` for feishu\n2. Remove the wecom channel or fix its channel ID\n\n\n3. Clean up the stale plugins and remove the duplicate feishu entry\n\nNow I'll write out the updated configuration.\n","thinkingSignature":"2331d31c2337f5fa63b6a825a0f7b51a66f9cda037111a209d7b372e47bb7064"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n现在处理。问题比较多，一个个来：\n\n**问题 1：飞书群消息被丢弃** — `groupPolicy: allowlist` 但 `groupAllowFrom` 空 → 改成 `open`\n**问题 2：wecom channel ID 不存在** — 需要删掉\n**问题 3：stale plugin references** — `wecom-openclaw-plugin` 指向已卸载的插件，清理掉\n**问题 4：重复 feishu 插件** — 干掉重复的\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yja7mv1sro5c_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":546,"output":304,"cacheRead":81728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82578,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777987363974,"responseId":"064922249de06cd01fbff2ffabba613a"}}
