{"type":"message","id":"04b8b114","parentId":"aedea4a5","timestamp":"2026-05-05T13:36:53.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what all these problems mean. Let me give a clear summary of what's broken and what needs to be fixed.\n","thinkingSignature":"bf0ba4263b0603fcca2ddb48cd6b65236e69134f3e7b4a1a150b86c56395b217"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n当前情况：\n\n**Gateway 能启动，但配置有残留问题：**\n\n1. **飞书** — 配置本身没问题，但有两处插件警告（重复 ID、缺编译产物），不影响使用\n2. **企业微信** — 插件已损坏（配置还在但实际无法加载），建议先禁用\n3. **微信** — 安装不完整，缺 TypeScript 编译产物，无法使用\n\n**一句话总结：**\n> 飞书能用，企业微信插件坏了，微信也坏了。\n\n---\n\n**要修复吗？**\n\n1. **清理残留** — 移除无效的 wecom/weixin 配置，我来做\n2. **修飞书插件** — 解决重复 ID 警告，需要重新安装飞书插件\n3. **都不管** — 飞书私聊够用，先放着\n\n你想怎么处理？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85187,"output":198,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85449,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777988200064,"responseId":"064925699161caf3f530f8087c888d5e"}}
