{"type":"message","id":"573bfec5","parentId":"706919fb","timestamp":"2026-05-05T13:43:00.084Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to:\n1. Uninstall/disable wecom and weixin\n2. Keep feishu working properly\n\nLet me clean up the config to remove all wecom/weixin references, then restart.","thinkingSignature":"674502deb8a5c29965d6a115bafa3de0ac54a88eae52a17be713a23a582daf45"},{"type":"text","text":"好，清理 wecom 和 weixin，保留飞书。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ir0ymlrt1vt2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\n# Remove wecom channel\nd['channels'].pop('wecom', None)\n# Remove stale plugin entries\nfor p in ['wecom-openclaw-plugin', 'openclaw-weixin']:\n    d['plugins']['entries'].pop(p, None)\n# Clean plugins.allow\nd['plugins']['allow'] = [x for x in d['plugins'].get('allow',[]) if x not in ['wecom', 'wecom-openclaw-plugin', 'openclaw-weixin']]\n# Remove invalid messages key\nd.pop('messages', None)\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json','w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\nprint('Done')\nprint('channels:', list(d['channels'].keys()))\nprint('plugins entries:', list(d['plugins']['entries'].keys()))\nprint('plugins allow:', d['plugins']['allow'])\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":152,"output":298,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":87947,"totalTokens":88397,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777988567786,"responseId":"064926d88006ba5f43a4e7d5ced04d3c"}}
