{"type":"message","id":"5e3fa286","parentId":"4ea4a7fb","timestamp":"2026-05-05T13:52:11.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good! Feishu is working now. The message was sent successfully. And the user just sent \"1\" which was a test message from Feishu that I received! Let me report back.\n","thinkingSignature":"72f961f30bb824cca661065ba194641401cf4f00241f6abb033a4fade7542bd7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n飞书双向通信搞定了 ✅\n\n刚才那条\"1\"就是从飞书发过来的——说明飞书现在收发自如。你在 web 端收到我刚发的确认消息了吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":173,"output":84,"cacheRead":87616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87873,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777989125934,"responseId":"064929066a07cf3b9fd6de888a4c6f6c"}}
