{"type":"message","id":"c563e804","parentId":"8bf8d13c","timestamp":"2026-05-05T13:52:45.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI is frustrated - they said \"爱玛，怎么总是不行啊，我都不敢给你升级了\" - which means \"Oh my god, it always doesn't work, I dare not upgrade you anymore.\" This is coming from Feishu (the chat_id shows user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb), so Feishu IS working now! The message came through from Feishu.\n\nThey're worried about upgrading because things keep breaking. I should:\n1. Acknowledge their frustration\n2. Confirm that Feishu IS working now (this message came through from Feishu!)\n3. Be honest about the upgrade risk\n\n\n4. Let them know it's okay to hold off on upgrading if they want to wait and see how things stabilize first\n","thinkingSignature":"9768abbaefeab3dbb7b7575a3e4e42027b4b5bd973b1a7ed01624d2c0aee2c69"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到！这条就是从飞书发过来的——飞书其实好了 ✅\n\n别慌，升级可以先停一停。让我看看当前版本和 staged 版本的差距：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4sz4nifowxir_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/package.json | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print('当前运行:', d.get('version',''))\"\n# Check if there's a newer version available\nopenclaw --version 2>&1 | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":675,"output":293,"cacheRead":87232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88200,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777989150162,"responseId":"0649291fb27b9664c2fe3471f36b5052"}}
