{"type":"message","id":"aa5f19d4","parentId":"dd9fa02a","timestamp":"2026-05-05T13:52:55.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"I'm scared to upgrade you now\" - implying that every upgrade causes problems. And indeed the staged openclaw (2026.3.23) was interfering with the working global (2026.5.4). The staged version was likely from a previous upgrade that left stale plugins behind.\n\nThe root issue was that there was a stale `.openclaw-install-stage-*` directory with an old version (2026.3.23) that was conflicting with the global installation (2026.5.4). This is an upgrade residue issue.\n\nNow I should acknowledge this and be honest. The system is working now. I shouldn't touch the upgrade process without understanding it better first.\n","thinkingSignature":"4ec1cf80a54afe8e1eb540475baf39ce9523768da82cc7427239a8349e702353"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n能理解你的担心。\n\n今天的问题根源是**升级残留**——之前升级时留下了一个旧版本（2026.3.23）的 staged 插件，和正式版本（2026.5.4）冲突，导致飞书报错 `Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'registry')`。\n\n刚清理掉了那个残留的 staged 插件，现在飞书正常了。\n\n**建议：**\n- 暂时不升级，等稳定了再说\n- 如果要升级，先跑 `openclaw doctor` 看看有没有残留再操作\n\n这次算是个教训——升级后最好检查一下有没有旧的残留目录。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":167,"output":266,"cacheRead":87872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88305,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777989166032,"responseId":"0649292eeb48e1fcfb674d24b578be1a"}}
