{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50abc80950a0c3cb3487fb93b81\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-05 22:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"704312ab","parentId":"12761177","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:02:23.040Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"b2e2b387","parentId":"704312ab","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:02:41.780Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the difference between cron and HEARTBEAT.md - both seem to do scheduled/periodic tasks. They're asking why we need HEARTBEAT.md if cron already handles timing.\n\nThis is a good question. Let me explain the difference clearly:\n\n**Cron (定时任务):**\n- For precise scheduling (\"每周一早上9点整\")\n- Runs in isolated sessions\n- Output goes to channel directly\n- Good for one-shot reminders or precise recurring tasks\n\n**HEARTBEAT.md:**\n- Batch checks multiple things at once when heartbeat fires (~every 30 min)\n- Uses the current conversation context\n- More flexible, can check multiple things together\n- Good for \"check if there's anything I need to act on\"\n\n\n- Essentially acts as a dynamic to-do list that gets reviewed during regular heartbeat intervals rather than running on a fixed schedule\n","thinkingSignature":"4ef20234ec664d79427a461a668f2eed0514af300ab3c77e6a81293476c68afb"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，两个都是定时触发，但用途不同：\n\n| | **Cron** | **HEARTBEAT.md** |\n|--|--|--|\n| 精度 | 精确时间（\"每周一9点整\"） | 约30分钟一次，灵活 |\n| 上下文 | 独立 session，无历史对话 | 用当前会话上下文 |\n| 场景 | 精确的提醒、一次性任务 | 需要批量检查多个事项 |\n| 输出 | 直接发到频道 | 通过会话返回 |\n\n**简单说：**\n- **Cron** = 闹钟，到点就响，不管你在不在\n- **HEARTBEAT** = 我每次醒来顺手看一眼有没有事要做\n\n比如你想让我\"每周一9点汇报周报\"→ Cron\n比如你想让我\"每次心跳检查一下有没有未读重要邮件\"→ HEARTBEAT.md\n\n两者不冲突，可以同时用。你现在有什么需要定期关注的事吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":478,"output":364,"cacheRead":98944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99786,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777989743040,"responseId":"06492b6fc5d5f1677fa4b8b36f7ef4e8"}}
