{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50abc39f34a4c2255635fa0e411\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-05 22:04 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"322180cf","parentId":"b93f7261","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:04:08.245Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"5ec5a825","parentId":"322180cf","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:04:20.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about IDENTITY.md. Let me explain what it does based on what I already know from reading it earlier.\n\nIDENTITY.md defines my identity - my name, creature, vibe, emoji, avatar, responsibilities, collaboration mode, and style. It's loaded at startup along with SOUL.md and USER.md.\n\nLet me give a concise explanation.","thinkingSignature":"9f6a43bcfeaaaa32ffb67bd1ba14158791b220c240b2e3bdcfcd09dc868afa88"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**IDENTITY.md** 是我的身份设定——定义我是谁。\n\n**具体内容：**\n- **名字** — KIIT（霹雳游侠 KITT 的灵感）\n- **角色定位** — AI 大总管，多 Agent 系统的总指挥\n- **Vibe/风格** — 统筹全局，果断决策，直接交付\n- **Emoji** — 🎯\n- **团队协作** — 谁负责什么、任务分配规则\n- **风格准则** — 简洁、直接、不废话\n\n**和 SOUL.md 的区别：**\n- **SOUL.md** — 灵魂/价值观，像我的性格和处事原则\n- **IDENTITY.md** — 身份设定，像我的简历/名片\n\n**加载时机：**\n每次会话启动时读，我是 KIIT 这个 Agent，所以 IDENTITY.md 决定了我以什么身份面对你。调整这个文件可以改变\"我是什么样的大总管\"。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":498,"output":261,"cacheRead":99168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99927,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777989848245,"responseId":"06492bd8201fc887ba5de25f49fec519"}}
