{"type":"message","id":"317375d0","parentId":"d2bd6b29","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:16:33.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The document only has 2 blocks - the document block and a page block (Heading 1 block). But the `raw_content` endpoint returned substantial content (1029 chars). Let me try a different approach to get all the document content.\n","thinkingSignature":"13f22ad944ffc8a93b032715cf1bac0be0e78ef0d9e11e055d13924fb3fb4ec1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pw9buvhqi3dp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"DOC_TOKEN=\"JQXqd7vIIoTe3jxPAZ0cBViYnNi\"\nTOKEN=\"t-g10455laLNCINI3M754RGERNY62VIV5LJLLRSJFJ\"\n\n# Get full raw content\ncurl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/${DOC_TOKEN}/raw_content\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\ncontent = d.get('data',{}).get('content','')\nprint(content)\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":483,"output":205,"cacheRead":115520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116208,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777990583709,"responseId":"06492eb89553fde9bd89285ede0108d5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c1afe05","parentId":"317375d0","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:16:33.981Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pw9buvhqi3dp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品方法论 v5.0\n# TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品方法论 v5.0\n## 融合亚马逊精铺三步验证法 + TK实战体系\n\n> **版本说明**：v5.0 = v4.0 框架 + 亚马逊精铺核心验证逻辑\n> **新增核心**：三步快速验证体系（精准词验可行性→竞价算成本→保守测盈利）+ 备货黄金法则\n> **市场**：越南(VN)为主 + 泰国(TH)为辅\n> **品类**：发饰（发夹/发箍/发圈/头绳/抓夹/发簪）\n\n---\n\n## 核心定位\n\n**精铺选品 = 重选品、轻运营、低风险、靠内容盈利**\n\n不靠运气，靠：\n**精准验证 + 微创新 + 差异化 + 变体合规循环 + 短视频种草能力**\n\n---\n\n## 零、选品总口诀（亚马逊+TK融合版）\n\n```\n参数卡死筛红海，\n精准词验证可行性，\n通用词深挖细分，\n小批量快跑控风险，\n内容种草接流量，\n不卷不烧稳稳赚。\n```\n\n---\n\n## 一、精准流量词 → TK精准标签词（一切分析的基础）\n\n### 亚马逊逻辑\n精准词 = 能精准描述功能、材质、特征、场景、对象的词\n\n### TK东南亚适配\n\n| 流量词类型 | 亚马逊 | TikTok Shop |\n|-----------|--------|-------------|\n| 核心词 | 搜索关键词 | Hashtag标签（越南语/泰语） |\n| 长尾词 | 精准属性词 | 场景词 + 人群词 + 用途词 |\n| 找竞品方式 | 关键词反查 | **达人视频标签反查** |\n\n### 精准标签词的作用（TK版本）\n1. **找到直接竞品** → 做市场/竞品分析\n2. **广告架构简单** → TK内容种草+小店闭环，转化有保障\n3. **反查流量成本** → 算短视频CPM/带货GMV投产比\n4. **判断真蓝海**：\n   - 小众 + 有精准标签 + 弱竞品 = **真蓝海**\n   - 小众 + 无精准标签 = 没市场\n\n### 标签词获取方法\n- EchoTik商品搜索 → 看关联标签\n- TikTok搜索 `$关键词 + 带货` → 看达人视频标签\n- 越南语/泰语本地化精准词（**必须本地语言！**）\n\n---\n\n## 二、核心参数卡死（源头过滤红海）—— 亚马逊精铺精髓\n\n> 亚马逊精铺第一步：用固定参数筛红海，从源头过滤大部分无效品\n> TK版"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":468,"aggregated":"TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品方法论 v5.0\n# TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品方法论 v5.0\n## 融合亚马逊精铺三步验证法 + TK实战体系\n\n> **版本说明**：v5.0 = v4.0 框架 + 亚马逊精铺核心验证逻辑\n> **新增核心**：三步快速验证体系（精准词验可行性→竞价算成本→保守测盈利）+ 备货黄金法则\n> **市场**：越南(VN)为主 + 泰国(TH)为辅\n> **品类**：发饰（发夹/发箍/发圈/头绳/抓夹/发簪）\n\n---\n\n## 核心定位\n\n**精铺选品 = 重选品、轻运营、低风险、靠内容盈利**\n\n不靠运气，靠：\n**精准验证 + 微创新 + 差异化 + 变体合规循环 + 短视频种草能力**\n\n---\n\n## 零、选品总口诀（亚马逊+TK融合版）\n\n```\n参数卡死筛红海，\n精准词验证可行性，\n通用词深挖细分，\n小批量快跑控风险，\n内容种草接流量，\n不卷不烧稳稳赚。\n```\n\n---\n\n## 一、精准流量词 → TK精准标签词（一切分析的基础）\n\n### 亚马逊逻辑\n精准词 = 能精准描述功能、材质、特征、场景、对象的词\n\n### TK东南亚适配\n\n| 流量词类型 | 亚马逊 | TikTok Shop |\n|-----------|--------|-------------|\n| 核心词 | 搜索关键词 | Hashtag标签（越南语/泰语） |\n| 长尾词 | 精准属性词 | 场景词 + 人群词 + 用途词 |\n| 找竞品方式 | 关键词反查 | **达人视频标签反查** |\n\n### 精准标签词的作用（TK版本）\n1. **找到直接竞品** → 做市场/竞品分析\n2. **广告架构简单** → TK内容种草+小店闭环，转化有保障\n3. **反查流量成本** → 算短视频CPM/带货GMV投产比\n4. **判断真蓝海**：\n   - 小众 + 有精准标签 + 弱竞品 = **真蓝海**\n   - 小众 + 无精准标签 = 没市场\n\n### 标签词获取方法\n- EchoTik商品搜索 → 看关联标签\n- TikTok搜索 `$关键词 + 带货` → 看达人视频标签\n- 越南语/泰语本地化精准词（**必须本地语言！**）\n\n---\n\n## 二、核心参数卡死（源头过滤红海）—— 亚马逊精铺精髓\n\n> 亚马逊精铺第一步：用固定参数筛红海，从源头过滤大部分无效品\n> TK版","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777990593980}}
{"type":"message","id":"ab33d74f","parentId":"3c1afe05","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:16:45.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The document has the first section but it's truncated. Let me try to get the full content. The document is quite long (SELECTION-METHOD-v5.0.md is 19KB). The raw_content API might have a size limit. Let me try to get all blocks via list_blocks and reconstruct the content.","thinkingSignature":"203c880479d8ee4b35f1937fdc80d2dc0557d932f8d7f50c8916e060324efc7f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vkrerxie1q3g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"DOC_TOKEN=\"JQXqd7vIIoTe3jxPAZ0cBViYnNi\"\nTOKEN=\"t-g10455laLNCINI3M754RGERNY62VIV5LJLLRSJFJ\"\n\n# Try list_blocks to get all content\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/${DOC_TOKEN}/blocks/${DOC_TOKEN}/children/search\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"query\":\"\",\"page_size\":100}' | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('code:', d.get('code'))\nitems = d.get('data',{}).get('items',[])\nprint('found:', len(items))\n\" 2>&1\n\n# Get blocks with text content by using the blocks list\ncurl -s -X GET \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/${DOC_TOKEN}/blocks?page_size=200&document_revision_id=-1\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\ndata = d.get('data',{})\nprint('items count:', len(data.get('items',[])))\nprint('has_more:', data.get('has_more'))\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":786,"output":389,"cacheRead":115968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777990593996,"responseId":"06492ec25e330e7650bc2c8d70a1f84e"}}
