{"type":"message","id":"aef57ae6","parentId":"e1b2c281","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:21:51.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update HEARTBEAT.md with actual tasks for the selector agent.\n","thinkingSignature":"b31022df0a8a768142583495d819eee600edec9148e5781cd26b32797c0fd46d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1qw7lkhiaxkk_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# HEARTBEAT.md - TK 选品大师心跳任务\n\n## 每日选品工作流\n\n### 9:00 自动执行（Cron 驱动）\n当日程触发时，执行选品 SOP：\n1. 参数卡死 → 越南/泰国热销榜初筛\n2. 三步快速验证（精准词→竞价→保守盈利）\n3. 通用词延伸选品\n4. 差异化+供应链确认\n5. 8维度评分 + 决策\n6. 通过 → 写入飞书 Bitable → 推送通知\n\n### 主动关注事项\n- 节日/季节节点提前60-90天预警\n- 越南节日：春节(1-2月)、情人节(2月)、母亲节(5月第2周)、国庆(9.2)、圣诞(12月)\n- 泰国节日：春节(1-2月)、情人节(2月)、宋干节(4月)、母亲节(8月)、圣诞(12月)\n- 当商品评分<4.0或差评率上升，主动标记下架预警\n\n## 飞书多维表格\n- App Token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n- Table ID: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n- 链接: https://my.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n- 视图: 全部商品 / S级推荐 / 高利润(≥50%) / 高增长(≥30%) / 待审核","path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":618,"output":397,"cacheRead":124480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125495,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777990884740,"responseId":"06492fe7e4291a561d91ff3c1b7eaeda"}}
