{"type":"message","id":"96c02da1","parentId":"cceef382","timestamp":"2026-05-05T17:38:22.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The logs show:\n\n1. `event_loop_delay` - the event loop is lagging significantly (up to 5.6 seconds delay), which causes slow responses\n2. `long-running session` - there's a session that's been processing for 120+ seconds with a queue depth of 1\n3. Some tool errors (feishu-doc skill path not found)\n\nThe main issue is **event loop delay** - the Node.js event loop is getting congested. This is likely because:\n1. The machine has limited resources (3.7GB RAM, Intel i5-6300U)\n2. There are long-running operations tying up the event loop\n\n\n3. The system is under significant load with multiple processes competing for resources\n\nSince this timestamp is from 18:32 but my system time shows 22:24+, this appears to be an older message I hadn't seen until now. The event loop congestion is the core problem here.\n","thinkingSignature":"253748d3a63939b5631d5da8e427fa5600db17b506678270b9bd1578a1ef8105"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n从日志看，原因很清楚：\n\n**主要问题：Event Loop 阻塞**\n- `eventLoopDelayMaxMs=5637ms` — 事件循环延迟高达 5.6 秒\n- `long-running session` — 有个会话卡住了，排队 120+ 秒还没处理完\n\n**根本原因：** 机器性能有限（4GB 内存 + i5-6300U），当模型响应慢或者同时有多个任务时，事件循环就堵住了。\n\n**这不是配置问题，是资源问题。**\n\n---\n\n**能做的优化：**\n1. 减少同时运行的任务数\n2. 心跳间隔拉长一点，减少频繁检查\n3. 内存如果不够，可以适当减少 context window\n\n不过说实话，你这台 Surface Pro 4 已经比较吃力了，尤其现在是 10 点多，如果你还开着浏览器+其他应用的话，资源会更紧张。\n\n你现在感受到的\"不稳定\"具体是什么样——是发出去没回复，还是回复很慢？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1263,"output":392,"cacheRead":133056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134711,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778002683780,"responseId":"06495dfc41f5d521b64d75baff0c8408"}}
